// Phase 22: CSS bundle, DOM/events, canvas, WASM/WebGL stubs.
samūhalakṣaṇaḥ css-āṇḍa vākyam body{color:blue} iti.
āhvānam std.web.css_bundle css-āṇḍa phalaṃ nidadhāti.
kośaḥ vṛkṣaḥ.
sthāpanam vṛkṣaḥ nodes iti kośaḥ.
āhvānam std.web.dom_dispatch vṛkṣaḥ vākyam #btn iti vākyam click iti phalaṃ nidadhāti.
āhvānam std.web.bridge_execute vākyam wasm iti vākyam (module) iti phalaṃ nidadhāti.
gaṇakaḥ phalaṃ darśayati.
